|:---------------------------------------------|--------:|-----:|------:|:-----|
|Instruction × Proficiency on participant mean |   -0.809| 0.486| -1.665|0.099 |
|Instruction × Proficiency on change score     |    0.526| 0.674|  0.780|0.437 |


