|Analysis         |Unit         | Mean difference (ms)| Statistic| df|p      |Generalizes to   |
|:----------------|:------------|--------------------:|---------:|--:|:------|:----------------|
|F1 (by-subjects) |participants |                 59.6|   -17.540| 39|< .001 |new participants |
|F2 (by-items)    |items        |                -59.6|    -2.516| 46|0.015  |new items        |


